    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, and rust, with paint that retains full gloss and even color throughout. The interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 seating surfaces, trim, and controls are all in original, unmarked condition. Mechanically, the vehicle has been well maintained with no known issues.",
